      "options": {},
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "flex": 1,
          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### For 60 years, one paradigm.\n\nYou click. You navigate. You learn where features hide.\n\n**The interface is fixed. You adapt to it.**\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 3,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "> *\"Intent-based outcome specification...the first new UI interaction paradigm in 60 years\"*\n>\n> **— IBM Research AI, 2024**"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "key": "TToraBdg",
      "options": {},
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "flex": 1,
          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Photoshop\n\n500 menu items and buttons\n\nYou use about 20\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 3,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "### 500 - 20 = 480\n\n## **Everyone Tax**\n\nYou pay cognitive load for 480 features you'll never use.\n\nEvery feature built for someone else is a burden you carry."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "key": "QuqqQGRh",
      "options": {},
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "flex": 1,
          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Your Last Research Session\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "You needed to understand something.\n\n**Browser** → Read articles (focus)\n\n**Switch to Excel** → Build dataset (context restart)\n\n**Switch to Python** → Run analysis (rebuild mental model)\n\n**Switch to Keynote** → Create visualization (start fresh)\n\n**4 apps. 4 cognitive restarts.**\n\nYour understanding fractured at every boundary."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "key": "QEyFfbgD",
      "options": {},
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "flex": 2,
          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 3,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n## What if interfaces moved with your thinking\n\n## instead of interrupting it?\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "key": "QreH51Zr",
      "options": {},
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "flex": 1,
          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Ephemeral Interfaces\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "Transient cognitive surfaces that:\n\n**Materialize** around your intent\n\n**Adapt** as context changes\n\n**Dissolve** when purpose is fulfilled\n\nNot fixed artifacts designed and shipped.\n\nLiving compositions generated on-demand."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
    {
      "key": "WWVt0OWP",
      "options": {},
      "sections": [
        {
          "type": "section",
          "flex": 1,
          "scrollable": false,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Purpose-Driven, Not Timer-Based\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "**Traditional:**\n- You pay a bill\n- Form stays open\n- You manually close it\n\n**Ephemeral:**\n- You pay a bill\n- Payment form appears (pre-filled)\n- You confirm\n- Payment processes\n- **Interface dissolves**\n\nNot because 60 seconds passed.\n\nBecause the purpose was fulfilled."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "comments": []
    },
