              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Traditional (Application-Centric)\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n1. Open browser → search\n2. Switch to spreadsheet → analyze\n3. Switch to charts → visualize\n4. Switch to presentation → create\n\n**4 apps. 4 context switches. 4 cognitive restarts.**\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "center",
              "flex": 1,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\n\n### Intent-Centric (Ephemeral)\n"
            },
            {
              "type": "column",
              "align": "centerLeft",
              "flex": 2,
              "scrollable": false,
              "content": "\"Explore ocean temperature trends\"\n\n→ Research environment materializes\n\n→ As inquiry shifts, environment reconfigures\n\n→ Question answered, surface dissolves\n\n**0 context switches. Continuous cognitive flow.**"
            }
          ]
        }
